# svn-npm-crutch-test

Dummy test project

## Getting Started
Install the module with: `npm install svn-npm-crutch-test`

```javascript
var svn_npm_crutch_test = require('svn-npm-crutch-test');
svn_npm_crutch_test.awesome(); // "awesome"
```
